---
title: Bulgogi-Style Pork Chops with Gingery Stir-Fried Bok Choy, Cabbage & Carrot
description: If you can’t get enough of Korean-inspired flavors, this meal is sure to leave you satisfied. The dish centers around savory-sweet bulgogi sauce, whisked with a bit of butter and spooned over succulent pork chops. There’s also a gingery stir-fry of bok choy, cabbage, and carrots on the side. Yeah, this meal has a little bit of something for everyone.
